Shift + Cmd + Del : permanently clear the garbage can
CMD + Space: start typing the name of the application + Enter to run

Ctrl + CMD + Space: Change input language

Space on a file: will do a quick-preview of file contents without opening it

CMD + Shift + 4: take a screenshot, after specifying the capture area
CMD + Shift + 3: desktop screenshot

CMD + Option + Space: "Search"
